Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
getDensityMapMode(25.10)                              getDensityMapMode(25.10)

Name
       getDensityMapMode

Syntax
       getDensityMapMode

       [-gridInMicron]

       [-gridInRow]

       [-ignoreBlock]

       [-ignoreFiller]

       [-quiet]

       [-threshold]

       Returns  the  information about setDensityMapMode parameters in the In-
       novus log file and in the Innovus console. Returns the following infor-
       mation.

              * Parameter name

              * Current value

              * Type (Boolean, string, and so on)

              * Source of current value (default, user)

       If you do not specify a parameter, the software displays values for all
       of the setDensityMapMode mode parameters.

Related Information
              * setDensityMapMode

              * Placing the Design chapter in Innovus User Guide.

